    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and I think you\u2019re going to love it! It\u2019s been such a dependable companion for me, and it\u2019s still in really wonderful shape and ready to hit the road. It drives smoothly, looks great, and has been well-cared for over the years. If you're looking for a solid, honest ride that won't let you down, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm excited to show it to you!",
