    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example is equipped with the preferred Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a functional M-Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. The suspension geometry is maintained by Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed bushings, providing the sharp turn-in and lateral stability expected of this chassis. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and light interior bolster wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization of the individual throttle bodies and the integrity of the cooling system make this a robust performer ready for spirited driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
